      "text": "Un winna Brahtu to ang-\nstako Tehwu bija diwifints /\ntschetrdefinits un tſchetri. Un\nAmasajus/ Asareêta Dehls / ta\nDehla Akusajus/ ta Dehla Me-\nfiltamota/ ta Dehla Immera.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Brahtu/ ſtip-\nro Wihru/ bija ſimts diwide-\nmits un aſtoni. Un tas Uhs-\nraugs pahr teem bija Sabdiels/\nGedolima Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no teem Lewiteem\nSefmajus/ Asuba Dehls / ta\nDehla Asrikama/ ta Dehla Aſa-\nbijus/ ta Dehla Bunnus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sabtajus/ un Joſa-\nbads no teem Wirſneekeem to\nLewitu/ btja pahr to Darbu Ah-\nrapuffê ta Deewa Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Matanijus/ Mikus\nDehls/ ta Dehla ſabdus/ ta\nde Dehla Affawa / bija tas pir-\nmajs/ kas Luhgſchanâ to Pateiſ-\nſchanu eefahze. Un Baƙbuki-\njus/ bija tas ohtrs no faaweem\nBrahteeim/ un Abdus/ Sam-\nmuifs Dehls/ ta Dehla Galala/\nta Dehla Jedutuna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſfo Lewitu tai fivehta\nPilsfahta/ bija diwifimts aſton-\ndesmits un tschetr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Wahrtu-Sargi\nAkubs/ Talmons ar faaweem\nBrahteeim teem Sargeem eekſch\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tee zitti no Israe-\nno teem Preestereem/ un teem\nwiteem/ bija wiſds Juhda P-\nsahtds / ikweens ſawâ Jh-\nchumâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Netininm dſihw-\neekſch Oweta/ un Zikus/ un G-\npus bija pahr teem Netininm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Lewitu Uhera-\neekſch Jeruſalemes / bija Uf-\nBanus Dehls/ ta Dehla Aſa-\njus/ ta Dehla Matanijus/\nDehla Mikus. No Aſa-\nBehrneem bija tee Dseed-\napkahrt to Darbu ta Dee-\nNamuna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta Kehnixa Ban-\nbija pahr teem/ ka teem Dsee-\ntajeem nhstizzigi ikdeenas i-\njadarra/ kaſteem Deenu pree-\nDeenas peenahzahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Petajus/ Mesabe-\nDehls/ no Šerus Behrne-\nta Dehla Juhda / bija pee-\nKehnixa Rohtas eekſch wiſa-\nLeetahm to Lauschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
